<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant-TW">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AI 小工具</title>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
</head>

<body class="body">
    <form action="/" method="post">
      <div class="card">
        <img
          src="https://www.wineontable.com.tw/upload/article/20190507/692994ccbfa5460aacece50e2e6b20f7/692994ccbfa5460aacece50e2e6b20f7.jpg"
          alt="pokemon_logo" class="card-img">
        <h1 class="card-title">請填入酒類或是飲料類別，<br>趕快為您的創意調酒取名稱吧!</h1>
        <p>(請勿輸入空白)</p>
        <p class="card-text">
          <% if (description.length) { %>
            <%= description %>
              <% } else { %>
                <%= '???' %>
                  <% } %>
        </p>
        <input type="text" name="description" class="card-input" placeholder="e.g. 蘭姆和柳橙汁" />
        <button type="submit" class="card-btn">送出</button>
      </div>
    </form>
</body>

</html>